\[CD^2 = 4x^2 + 36 - 12x \cos 20^\circ.\]Hence, $4x^2 = 36,$ so $x = 3 \sqrt{2}.$

Then $DE = 6 - x = 6 - 3 \sqrt{2},$ and $BF = 2x = 6 \sqrt{2}.$

